### Test all API endpoints from VS Code

### Install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client) to run these

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Baseline prediction (no privacy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict/plain
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "income": 50000,
  "credit_score": 720,
  "debt": 10000,
  "employment_years": 5
}

###

### Prediction with Differential Privacy
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict/private
Content-Type: application/json  

{
  "income": 50000,
  "credit_score": 720,
  "debt": 10000,
  "employment_years": 5
}

###

### High-risk applicant
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict/private
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "income": 25000,
  "credit_score": 480,
  "debt": 35000,
  "employment_years": 0.5
}

###

### Check privacy budget
GET {{baseUrl}}/epsilon
